(8, 'IT Operations Technical Lead', 32, 2, 1, '5', 1, '<p>&bull; Bachelor Degree/Master in IT and/or Business Administration (CGPA &gt; 3.5 or similar grading is a must) with at least 5 years working experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; SAP and ERP experience is essential. Experience in SAP Solution Manager would be an added advantage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; With ITIL certified would be an added advantage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Strong in reporting skills in providing systems overview and monthly statistic. &bull; Fluent in English (verbally and written).</p>\r\n', 5, '5 & 6 Jalan KP 1/8, Kajang Prima, 43000 ', '', '<p>&bull; The IT Operations Technical Lead reports directly to the IT Operations Team Lead.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Managing the resolutions for all IT incidents with adequate know how.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Understanding of Systems Optimization and Monitoring with at least SAP Basis knowledge, eg: handling of system performance, error analysis skills &amp; etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Proven capabilities in safeguarding of IT critical systems and services, with understanding the importance of IT Reliability.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Analyze Systems report and provide a proposal of overall systems improvement &amp; stability.</p>\r\n', '<p>&bull; To coach a team of IT Operations Analyst ensures critical IT Processes continue to run 24/7 worldwide.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Manage a proactive team, ensuring clear team objectives and team responsibilities through efficient management and strong IT Problem Solving Skills.</p>\r\n', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'MYR', '3000.00', '5000.00', 0, 0, '2016-04-06 20:02:46', '2016-05-24 01:09:05', '2018-05-01', 'post', 0, 0, '2016-05-24 01:09:05'),
(9, 'Ecommerce Marketing Executive', 551, 3, 1, '2', 0, '• Fresh Graduate or those with 1-2 years in Business E-commerce, Marketing, PR or\r\nrelevant field is encourage to apply.\r\n• Familiarity with Malaysia Internet communities such as popular forums, blogs, online\r\nmarketplace and e-commerce websites.\r\n• Proficiency in English & Bahasa Malaysia.\r\n• Ability to speak / writing in Chinese will be an added advantage. • Skills in e-Commerce & e-Marketing are essential.\r\n• Strong interpersonal and communication skills.\r\n• Have positive and learning attitudes\r\n• Able to show initiative and to work with minimum supervision.\r\n• Able to work under pressure and a great team player.\r\n• Applicants must be willing to work at I-City, Shah Alam.\r\n• Must possess own transport.', 5, 'E-28-1, Jalan Multimedia 7/AG, City Park', '', '<p>&bull; To consult and assists merchants to generate revenue target<br />\r\n&bull; Develop strategic marketing plans and activities with merchants<br />\r\n&bull; Planning attractive online campaigns and events<br />\r\n&bull; Planning attractive campaigns and events in media social (Facebook, Wechat,<br />\r\nIntagram...)<br />\r\n&bull; Set target revenues and each process KPI with merchants<br />\r\n&bull; Provide solutions to achieve the target.<br />\r\n&bull; Provide e-commerce knowledge and information to merchants<br />\r\n&bull; Contributes to team effort by accomplishing related results as needed.<br />\r\n&bull; Motivate and empower the merchants to achieve their goal.<br />\r\n&bull; Any other duties as assigned by the Superior from time to time.<br />\r\n&bull; Engage actively in pre-sales activities</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'MYR', '2000.00', '3500.00', 0, 0, '2016-04-11 23:32:15', '2016-04-29 01:04:18', '2018-05-01', 'post', 0, 0, '2016-04-29 01:04:18'),
(10, 'Customer Support Executive', 551, 1, 1, '2', 0, '• Fresh Graduate or those with 1-2 years in Business E-commerce, Marketing, PR or\r\nrelevant field is encourage to apply.\r\n• Knowledge in computer skill\r\n• Proficiency in English & Bahasa Malaysia.\r\n• Ability to speak / writing in Chinese will be an added advantage. • Resolving Conflict & Problem Solving\r\n• Strong interpersonal and communication skills.\r\n• Have positive and learning attitudes\r\n• Able to show initiative and to work with minimum supervision. • Able to work under pressure and a great team player.\r\n• Applicants must be willing to work at I-City, Shah Alam.\r\n• Job training will be provided', 5, 'E-28-1, Jalan Multimedia 7/AG, City Park', '', '<p>&bull; Assist on new webstore setup, ensure the progress complete on time<br />\r\n&bull; Handle and support merchants&rsquo; enquiries via phone call, email and live chat.<br />\r\n&bull; Provide system training to merchant<br />\r\n&bull; Provide guideline and idea on how to increase online sales to merchant.<br />\r\n&bull; Provide guideline and idea on how to create social media to merchants<br />\r\n&bull; Coordinate with E-commerce consultant on marketing plans and activities with merchants &bull; Coordinate with data entry to ensure merchant&rsquo;s product uploading to website on time<br />\r\n&bull; Prepare Weekly E-mail blasting to customers<br />\r\n&bull; Prepare Weekly Merchant Sales Report<br />\r\n&bull; Any other duties as assigned by the Superior from time to time.<br />\r\n&bull; Engage actively in pre-sales activities</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'MYR', '2500.00', '3500.00', 0, 0, '2016-04-12 01:15:02', '2016-04-29 01:04:13', '2018-05-01', 'post', 0, 0, '2016-04-29 01:04:13'),
(11, 'Online Customer Service Executive', 551, 3, 1, '1-', 0, '• Minimum SPM or higher\r\n• Knowledge in computer skill\r\n• Proficiency in English & Bahasa Malaysia.\r\n• Ability to speak / writing in Chinese will be an added advantage. • Resolving Conflict & Problem Solving\r\n• Strong interpersonal and communication skills.\r\n• Have positive and learning attitudes\r\n• Able to show initiative and to work with minimum supervision.\r\n• Able to work under pressure and a great team player.\r\n• Applicants must be willing to work at I-City, Shah Alam.\r\n• Job training will be provided', 5, 'E-28-1, Jalan Multimedia 7/AG, City Park', '', '<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Serves customers by providing product, order and service information; resolving product, order and service problems.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Job Duties:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Handle and support customers&rsquo; enquiries via phone call, email and live chat instantly. &bull; Provide guideline / information / solutions about order, products and services.<br />\r\n&bull; Resolves order, product or service problems by clarifying the customer&#39;s complaint;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>determining the cause of the problem; selecting and explaining the best solution to solve the problem; expediting correction or adjustment; following up to ensure resolution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Handle online and offline orders which is incomplete status, ensure orders completed on time</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Provide guideline/ educate on how to update / complete order to seller/merchant. &bull; Prepares weekly sales reports<br />\r\n&bull; Contributes to team effort by accomplishing related results as needed.<br />\r\n&bull; Any other duties as assigned by the Superior from time to time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Engage actively in pre-sales activities&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'MYR', '2000.00', '2500.00', 0, 0, '2016-04-12 01:19:34', '2016-04-29 01:04:09', '2018-05-01', 'post', 0, 0, '2016-04-29 01:04:09'),
(12, 'Admin Executive', 551, 3, 1, '1', 0, '• Minimum SPM or higher\r\n• Knowledge in computer skill\r\n• Proficiency in English & Bahasa Malaysia.\r\n• Ability to speak / writing in Chinese will be an added advantage. • Resolving Conflict & Problem Solving\r\n• Strong interpersonal and communication skills.\r\n• Have positive and learning attitudes\r\n• Able to show initiative and to work with minimum supervision.\r\n• Able to work under pressure and a great team player.\r\n• Applicants must be willing to work at I-City, Shah Alam.\r\n• Job training will be provided', 5, '', '', '<p>Bring your work experience where people love to shop! Youbeli is a chain of full service department stores serving the total family needs of our customers. For over 10 years, Youbeli has been known for its great values and famous brands, and for offering a broad selection of quality merchandise in its stores and online. We are looking for an E-Commerce Data Entry role to join our team.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As part of a fast-paced, dynamic team, you will support our electronic commerce environment. Your previous experience along with your strong computer skills will ensure your success in this dynamic role. If you are looking for a great opportunity to pursue a rewarding career with a company known for quality and big savings, apply today!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Job Descriptions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Key in Product information which is provided by merchant to system and ensure product uploading to website on time</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Ensure all the information is correct before publish to website<br />\r\n&bull; Provide guideline on how to upload product to merchant.<br />\r\n&bull; Responsible for monitoring / enhance the quality of the product photos in website<br />\r\n&bull; Assist with Merchant Support/ E-commerce consultant when launching online campaigns&nbsp;and events<br />\r\n&bull; Prepare Weekly Product Arrival Report<br />\r\n&bull; Any other duties as assigned by the Superior from time to time. &bull; Engage actively in pre-sales activities</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'MYR', '1500.00', '2000.00', 0, 0, '2016-04-12 01:21:55', '2016-04-29 01:04:03', '2018-05-01', 'post', 0, 0, '2016-04-29 01:04:03'),
(13, 'Android/ios Mobile App Developer', 551, 3, 1, '2', 0, '• Required tool(s): Eclipse/ Xcode.\r\n• Required skill(s): Java/ Objective C.\r\n• SkilledinUI/UXtechniqueformobileapps\r\n• GoodunderstandingofHTML5,Javascript,JqueryandPHP\r\n• FamiliarwithNativeAppsDevelopment\r\n• Excellentdebuggingandoptimizationskills.\r\n• Abilitytoworkinateamenviroment.\r\n• Requiredlanguage(s):English,(AddedAdvantage-Chinese)\r\n• Atleast1year(s)ofworkingexperienceintherelatedfieldisrequiredforthisposition.\r\n• PreferablySeniorExecutivesspecializinginIT/Computer-Softwareorrequivalent.\r\n• FreshGraduatesalsoencouragetoapplyforjuniorpositions\r\n• Applicants must be willing to work at I-City, Shah Alam.\r\n• 3Full-Timeposition(s)available.', 5, 'E-28-1, Jalan Multimedia 7/AG, City Park', '', '<p>&bull; To design, develop and maintain IOS mobile appliacation<br />\r\n&bull; To studies and provide solution to clients requirements .<br />\r\n&bull; Work with different team to define, design and updates new features.<br />\r\n&bull; Work with leading APIs or SDKs to create or extend appliacation functionalities.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'MYR', '2500.00', '4000.00', 0, 0, '2016-04-12 01:25:09', '2016-04-29 01:03:58', '2018-05-01', 'post', 0, 0, '2016-04-29 01:03:58'),
