(41, 'Online Marketing Manager', 604, 2, 1, '1', 14, '<p>You love food and you love cohort analysis?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Awesome, you found the right spot here!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Launched in early 2015 by passionate foodies, tech geeks and ex-Rocket guys we have raised several rounds of VC funding from reputable investors to change the way people eat in SEA forever.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are building our online marketing team and you have the unique chance to be among the first to join and leave your mark in a fast growing food tech startup.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong style=\"line-height:1.6\">That&#39;s you:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>at least 1.5 years experience in online marketing at leading startup or ecommerce company (think VC backed or any Rocket Internet venture) or a highly analytical role</li>\r\n	<li>You have launched, maintained and managed campaigns on either FB &amp; IG, Adwords or GDN. You are extremely comfortable in tracking via GA, GTM or similar tools</li>\r\n	<li>vlookup and pivot tables are your friends</li>\r\n	<li>Hard working and hungry (not just for food)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How to apply:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Find out how much web traffic we had in May &#39;16</li>\r\n	<li>Tell us how you would double it in 1 month</li>\r\n	<li>Tell us why we should not do that and what we should do instead.</li>\r\n	<li>How does your favourite Saturday look like?</li>\r\n	<li>Send all answers to the previous questions together with your linkedin profile to jon(at)dahmakan.com</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>We strongly believe in equal opportunities, meritocracy and value diversity in our team. We do not discriminate on the basis of race, religion, color, national origin, gender, sexual orientation, age, marital status, or disability status.</p>\r\n', 6, '', '', '<p><strong>Your mission:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Strategise about new creative campaigns</li>\r\n	<li>Develop, implement and maintain ad campaigns</li>\r\n	<li>Help recruit our marketing team</li>\r\n	<li>Break down data to find out what really works</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why joining us:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Exciting growth phase of a food tech startup</li>\r\n	<li>Passionate and ambitious team</li>\r\n	<li>Flat team structures and immediate responsibility</li>\r\n	<li>Free lunch and dinner made by our Executive Chef</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'MYR', '1.00', '2.00', 0, 0, '2016-08-15 01:04:15', '2016-08-21 09:55:47', '2018-05-01', 'draft', 0, 0, '2016-08-21 09:55:47'),
(42, 'Chief Marketing Officer', 604, 3, 1, '5', 2, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>dahmakan is one of the fastest growing food tech startups in Asia with the simple mission to change the way we eat forever.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We use latest mobile and routing technology to simplify everyday lunch and dinner for millions of people.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We revolutionise the food industry by making food delivery more convenient, healthier and more affordable than it has ever been before.Funded and supported by leading global VCs, we are expanding fast across Asia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As Chief Marketing Officer you will become a co-founder and lead our growth and marketing team.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What we expect:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>At least 5 years experience in a marketing leadership position and clear track record of success and achievements</li>\r\n		<li>Deep understanding of all online channels (FB/IG, SEM, GDN, remarketing, affiliates) and offline channels</li>\r\n		<li>Highly structured and organised with an iterative and experimental mindset</li>\r\n		<li>Analytical and data driven: you don&rsquo;t make decisions based on gut feeling but clear testing</li>\r\n		<li>Experienced in analytics and all kind of tracking tools, an excel expert</li>\r\n		<li>A leader, ready to inspire and motivate your team to excel</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How to join:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Get in touch via jon(at)dahmakan.com</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The role is based in SEA/Malaysia.</p>\r\n', 6, '', '', '<p><strong>Lead our growth:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Build your growth team and hire the sharpest minds in marketing, growth and analytics</li>\r\n		<li>Implement best practices, marketing processes, structures, tracking and metrics</li>\r\n		<li>Lead strategic partnership and branding campaigns</li>\r\n		<li>Test, test and test!</li>\r\n		<li>Deep dive into customer behaviour, lifetime, frequency, retention and steer with Jessica (COO) and Chris (CTO) the product development roadmap</li>\r\n		<li>Set the regional expansion strategy with Jonathan (CEO)</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li>Create a holistic marketing approach to engage and retain customers across all channels</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why joining us:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Most senior leadership role in marketing with co-founder responsibilities, key member of the company growth</li>\r\n	<li>Exciting growth phase of a industry changing food startup</li>\r\n	<li>Salary and equity, we want that you own what you build</li>\r\n	<li>Passionate and ambitious team, daily meals by a Hilton Executive Chef</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'MYR', '1.00', '2.00', 0, 0, '2016-08-15 01:18:31', '2016-08-21 09:55:24', '2018-05-01', 'draft', 0, 0, '2016-08-21 09:55:24'),
(43, 'Business Developer Manager', 604, 3, 1, '3', 0, '<p>You love food and you love closing exciting partnerships?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Awesome, you found the right spot here!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>dahmakan was launched in early 2015 by passionate foodies, tech geeks and ex-Rocket guys.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have raised several rounds of VC funding from leading investors to change the way people eat in SEA forever.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are building our business development team and you have the rare chance to be among the first in our BD team.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Join our BD force and leave your mark in Malaysia&#39;s fastest growing food tech startup.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 6, '', '', '<p><strong>That&#39;s you:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>extrovert personality: you love meeting people and they like you</li>\r\n	<li>a born salesman without appearing to be sleazy or &ldquo;salesy&rdquo;</li>\r\n	<li>you want to work performance based with goals and metrics</li>\r\n	<li>highly competitive and drive to win</li>\r\n	<li>you rather pick up the phone than writing emails</li>\r\n	<li>&quot;All action&quot; attitude, only results and closing deals count</li>\r\n	<li>result driven and methodical &nbsp;- you learn from failure to continuously improve your approach</li>\r\n	<li>Hard working and hungry (not just for food)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How to apply:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Tell us about an exciting partnership that we should pursue</li>\r\n	<li>Draft an email to convince the target company/ person to engage in the partnership</li>\r\n	<li>Send us the answer to 1) &amp; 2) together with your linkedin profile to jon(at)dahmakan.com</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Your mission:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Develop creative partnerships to make our delicious food universally available</li>\r\n	<li>Build a network of new distribution channels and partners</li>\r\n	<li>Meet large corporations, government institutions, charities, media companies and celebrities</li>\r\n	<li>Execute campaigns with major F&amp;B and consumer brands</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why joining us:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Exciting growth phase of a food tech startup</li>\r\n		<li>Meritocracy: only smart ideas, execution and results count</li>\r\n		<li>We select our team based on attitude and drive, not experience or age</li>\r\n		<li>Passionate, hardworking and talented team</li>\r\n		<li>Flat team structures and immediate responsibility</li>\r\n		<li>Bonus: Free lunch and dinner made by our Executive Chef</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'MYR', '1.00', '2.00', 0, 0, '2016-08-15 01:38:26', '2016-08-21 09:55:11', '2018-05-01', 'draft', 0, 0, '2016-08-21 09:55:11'),
