(45, 'Corporate Sales Manager', 604, 3, 1, '2', 24, '', 6, '', '', '<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif\">You love food and you love closing exciting partnerships? Awesome, you found the right spot here!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif\">dahmakan was launched in early 2015 by passionate foodies, tech geeks and ex-Rocket guys. We have raised several rounds of VC funding from leading investors to change the way people eat in SEA forever.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif\">We are building our business development team and you have the rare chance to be among the first in our BD team. Join our BD force and leave your mark in Malaysia&#39;s fastest growing food tech startup.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif\"><strong>Your mission:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif\">Develop creative partnerships to make our delicious food universally available</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif\">Build a network of new distribution channels and partners</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif\">Meet large corporations, government institutions, charities, media companies and celebrities</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif\">Execute campaigns with major F&amp;B and consumer brands</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif\"><strong>Why joining us:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif\">Exciting growth phase of a food tech startup</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<l