(51, 'Senior Full Stack Developer', 604, 1, 1, '1', 0, '<p><strong>Why dahmakan:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our mission is to make eating healthy ridiculously simple. Three clicks and delicious food will be with you. We are a&nbsp;<strong>tech company</strong>&nbsp;and are using intelligent systems in all areas of our business. You get to work with our international team based in Kuala Lumpur on exciting problems related to machine learning and optimization. Working at dahmakan will empower you to use cutting edge technologies and frameworks, such as Spring Boot, AngularJS, TensorFlow and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Developing new IT products and features.</li>\r\n	<li>Deep understanding of technical challenges (optimization problems, machine learning, REST APIs).</li>\r\n	<li>You will be a central pillar in our development team (both in-house locally and our remote team).</li>\r\n	<li>Your main responsibilities will include DevOps, architectural decisions, mentoring our junior developers and release management.</li>\r\n	<li>You will be able to teach other developers with your excellent coding skills via code reviews but also by coding yourself business critical features.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Experience in the development of large systems.</li>\r\n	<li>Ideally Java Spring and web technologies such as AngularJS.</li>\r\n	<li>Experience in app development (iOS and Android) is preferred.</li>\r\n	<li>Experience with Scrum or some other agile development method.</li>\r\n	<li>Understanding of git, build servers and continuous integration preferred.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'MYR', '1.00', '2.00', 0, 0, '2016-08-29 19:59:36', '2016-08-29 19:59:36', '2018-05-01', 'draft', 0, 0, NULL),
(52, 'Tech Lead', 604, 1, 1, '1', 0, '<p><strong>Why dahmakan:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our mission is to make eating healthy ridiculously simple. Three clicks and delicious food will be with you. We are a&nbsp;<strong>tech company</strong>&nbsp;and are using intelligent systems in all areas of our business. You get to work with our international team based in Kuala Lumpur on exciting problems related to machine learning and optimization. Working at dahmakan will empower you to use cutting edge technologies and frameworks, such as Spring Boot, AngularJS, TensorFlow and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Developing new IT products and features.</li>\r\n	<li>Deep understanding of technical challenges (optimization problems, machine learning).</li>\r\n	<li>Building and managing a team of developers. Building large applications with clean architecture.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Experience in the development of large systems.</li>\r\n	<li>Java.</li>\r\n	<li>Web Technologies.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'MYR', '1.00', '2.00', 0, 0, '2016-08-29 20:05:22', '2016-08-29 20:05:22', '2018-05-01', 'draft', 0, 0, NULL),
(53, 'Senior Growth Manager', 604, 2, 1, '1', 14, '<p>You love food and even more,you love fast growth?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Awesome, you found the right spot here!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>dahmakan was launched in early 2015 by passionate foodies, tech geeks and ex-Rocket guys. We have raised several rounds of VC funding from reputable investors to change the way people eat in SEA forever.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As Senior Growth Manager you will lead our growth and marketing team together with our CMO.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lead our growth:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Build our growth team and hire the best in marketing, growth, analytics, design, content, business development and corporate sales</li>\r\n		<li>Develop together with our CMO a 12 month marketing plan and lead the execution</li>\r\n		<li>Support in setting up all marketing processes, structures, tracking and metrics</li>\r\n		<li>Conduct customer interviews and research</li>\r\n		<li>Develop creative offline marketing and lead online marketing channels</li>\r\n		<li>Work with Jessica (COO) and Chris (CTO) to prioritise product improvements and the development roadmap</li>\r\n		<li>Work with Jonathan (CEO) on growth strategy and investor reportings</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why joining us:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Senior role in marketing, key member for the company growth</li>\r\n	<li>Salary + equity: We want that you have ownership in a fast growing company</li>\r\n	<li>Exciting growth phase of a food tech startup</li>\r\n	<li>Passionate and ambitious team</li>\r\n	<li>We work and party together</li>\r\n	<li>Free lunch and dinner made by our Executive Chef</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What we expect from you:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>at least 2 years experience in marketing or you have lead a team in either a creative or number driven functions</li>\r\n		<li>Vlookup and pivot tables are your friends</li>\r\n		<li>Unicorn: you are both number affine and very creative</li>\r\n		<li>Highly analytical and data driven: you don&rsquo;t make decisions based on gut feeling</li>\r\n		<li>Experienced in analytics and tracking tools such as GA</li>\r\n		<li>Hard working and hungry (not just for food)</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'MYR', '1.00', '2.00', 0, 0, '2016-08-29 20:12:23', '2016-08-29 20:12:23', '2018-05-01', 'draft', 0, 0, NULL),
(54, 'Online Marketing Manager', 604, 1, 1, '1', 0, '<p>You love food and you love cohort analysis?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Awesome, you found the right spot here!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Launched in early 2015 by passionate foodies, tech geeks and ex-Rocket guys we have raised several rounds of VC funding from reputable investors to change the way people eat in SEA forever.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are building our online marketing team and you have the unique chance to be among the first to join and leave your mark in a fast growing food tech startup.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Your mission:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Strategise about new creative campaigns</li>\r\n	<li>Develop, implement and maintain ad campaigns</li>\r\n	<li>Help recruit our marketing team</li>\r\n	<li>Break down data to find out what really works</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why joining us:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Exciting growth phase of a food tech startup</li>\r\n	<li>Passionate and ambitious team</li>\r\n	<li>Flat team structures and immediate responsibility</li>\r\n	<li>Free lunch and dinner made by our Executive Chef</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>That&#39;s you:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>at least 1.5 years experience in online marketing at leading startup or ecommerce company (think VC backed or any Rocket Internet venture) or a highly analytical role</li>\r\n	<li>You have launched, maintained and managed campaigns on either FB &amp; IG, Adwords or GDN. You are extremely comfortable in tracking via GA, GTM or similar tools</li>\r\n	<li>vlookup and pivot tables are your friends</li>\r\n	<li>Hard working and hungry (not just for food)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How to apply:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Find out how much web traffic we had in May &#39;16</li>\r\n	<li>Tell us how you would double it in 1 month</li>\r\n	<li>Tell us why we should not do that and what we should do instead.</li>\r\n	<li>How does your favourite Saturday look like?</li>\r\n	<li>Send all answers to the previous questions together with your linkedin profile to jon(at)dahmakan.com</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>We strongly believe in equal opportunities, meritocracy and value diversity in our team. We do not discriminate on the basis of race, religion, color, national origin, gender, sexual orientation, age, marital status, or disability status.</p>\r\n', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'MYR', '1.00', '2.00', 0, 0, '2016-08-29 20:21:50', '2016-08-29 20:21:50', '2018-05-01', 'draft', 0, 0, NULL),
(55, 'Chief Marketing Officer', 604, 1, 1, '1', 0, '<p>dahmakan is one of the fastest growing food tech startups in Asia with the simple mission to change the way we eat forever.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We use latest mobile and routing technology to simplify everyday lunch and dinner for millions of people.We revolutionise the food industry by making food delivery more convenient, healthier and more affordable than it has ever been before.Funded and supported by leading global VCs, we are expanding fast across Asia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As Chief Marketing Officer you will become a co-founder and lead our growth and marketing team.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Lead our growth:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Build your growth team and hire the sharpest minds in marketing, growth and analytics</li>\r\n		<li>Implement best practices, marketing processes, structures, tracking and metrics</li>\r\n		<li>Lead strategic partnership and branding campaigns</li>\r\n		<li>Test, test and test!</li>\r\n		<li>Deep dive into customer behaviour, lifetime, frequency, retention and steer with Jessica (COO) and Chris (CTO) the product development roadmap</li>\r\n		<li>Set the regional expansion strategy with Jonathan (CEO)</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li>Create a holistic marketing approach to engage and retain customers across all channels</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why joining us:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Most senior leadership role in marketing with co-founder responsibilities, key member of the company growth</li>\r\n	<li>Exciting growth phase of a industry changing food startup</li>\r\n	<li>Salary and equity, we want that you own what you build</li>\r\n	<li>Passionate and ambitious team, daily meals by a Hilton Executive Chef</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What we expect:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>At least 5 years experience in a marketing leadership position and clear track record of success and achievements</li>\r\n		<li>Deep understanding of all online channels (FB/IG, SEM, GDN, remarketing, affiliates) and offline channels</li>\r\n		<li>Highly structured and organised with an iterative and experimental mindset</li>\r\n		<li>Analytical and data driven: you don&rsquo;t make decisions based on gut feeling but clear testing</li>\r\n		<li>Experienced in analytics and all kind of tracking tools, an excel expert</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'MYR', '1.00', '2.00', 0, 0, '2016-08-29 20:27:45', '2016-08-29 20:27:45', '2018-05-01', 'draft', 0, 0, NULL),
(56, 'Business Developer Manager', 604, 1, 1, '1', 0, '<p>You love food and you love closing exciting partnerships?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Awesome, you found the right spot here!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>dahmakan was launched in early 2015 by passionate foodies, tech geeks and ex-Rocket guys. We have raised several rounds of VC funding from leading investors to change the way people eat in SEA forever.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are building our business development team and you have the rare chance to be among the first in our BD team. Join our BD force and leave your mark in Malaysia&#39;s fastest growing food tech startup.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Your mission:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Develop creative partnerships to make our delicious food universally available</li>\r\n	<li>Build a network of new distribution channels and partners</li>\r\n	<li>Meet large corporations, government institutions, charities, media companies and celebrities</li>\r\n	<li>Execute campaigns with major F&amp;B and consumer brands</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why joining us:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>Exciting growth phase of a food tech startup</li>\r\n		<li>Meritocracy: only smart ideas, execution and results count</li>\r\n		<li>We select our team based on attitude and drive, not experience or age</li>\r\n		<li>Passionate, hardworking and talented team</li>\r\n		<li>Flat team structures and immediate responsibility</li>\r\n		<li>Bonus: Free lunch and dinner made by our Executive Chef</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>That&#39;s you:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>extrovert personality: you love meeting people and they like you</li>\r\n	<li>a born salesman without appearing to be sleazy or &ldquo;salesy&rdquo;</li>\r\n	<li>you want to work performance based with goals and metrics</li>\r\n	<li>highly competitive and drive to win</li>\r\n	<li>you rather pick up the phone than writing emails</li>\r\n	<li>&quot;All action&quot; attitude, only results and closing deals count</li>\r\n	<li>result driven and methodical &nbsp;- you learn from failure to continuously improve your approach</li>\r\n	<li>Hard working and hungry (not just for food)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How to apply:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Tell us about an exciting partnership that we should pursue</li>\r\n	<li>Draft an email to convince the target company/ person to engage in the partnership</li>\r\n	<li>Send us the answer to 1) &amp; 2) together with your linkedin profile to jon(at)dahmakan.com</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'MYR', '1.00', '2.00', 0, 0, '2016-08-29 20:41:50', '2016-08-29 20:41:50', '2018-05-01', 'draft', 0, 0, NULL),
