(152, 'Intern / Internship / Latihan Industri / Praktikal', 944, 1, 5, '0', 2, '<p>Requirements:</p><p>1. Undergraduate or degree or diploma or certificate or equivalent majoring in Business / Economics/ Property Management / Accounts or any Art or Science Discipline.</p><p>2. We are looking for independent, creative, mature, hardworking, eager to learn, energetic, pleasant personality and friendly and equip with good Microsoft office skills.</p><p>3. Candidate must be dynamic with good self-confidence and good communication skills as they will be dealing with our High Net worth Client.&nbsp;</p><p>4. You will participate in all business management in the company. Assist in business administration. Do market research. Analyse peer competitors. Create business proposal from the researched done.</p>', 6, '7-1, Jalan Solaris 3, Solaris Mont Kiara', '', '<p>Kami ingin membuka peluang kepada pelajar-pelajar universiti atau kolej tempatan yang berminat untuk menjalani latihan praktikal di organisasi kami.&nbsp;</p><p>Permohonan adalah dibuka sepanjang tahun.</p><p>Lelaki atau perempuan</p><p>Skop kerja adalah seperti berikut:</p><p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Membantu dalam segala aktiviti dikelolakan syarikat</p><p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Membantu dalam admin harian&nbsp;</p><p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Lakukan analisis pemasaran</p><p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Menganalisis pemasaran pesaing</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Pelatih haruslah mempunyai kemahiran komunikasi lisan dan bertulis yang sangat baik dengan berbekalkan pengetahuan luas tentang web dan media sosial.</p><p>PowerPoint, Word dan Excel pengalaman adalah bonus, dan akan dipertimbangkan apabila memilih pemohon yang terbaik untuk jawatan latihan ini.<br />&nbsp;</p><p>Bagi mereka yang berminat, sila emelkan :</p><p>a) Resume</p><p>b) Tempoh latihan</p><p>Di email genlauproperty36@gmail.com</p><p>Waktu pejabat Isnin-Jumaat 9:30 pagi-6:30 petang sahaja.</p><p>Elaun Bulanan ialah RM500</p><p>* Hanya calon yang disenarai pendek akan dipanggil untuk temuduga*</p><p>Pengambilan pelajar Latihan industri ini terbuka sepanjang tahun kepada semua pemegang sijil, diploma dan ijazah yang berminat untuk menyertai latihan intern / latihan praktikal / latihan industri / latihan praktikal</p><p>Terma &amp; Syarat tambahan: Perlu mempunyai pengangkutan sendiri atau menaiki bas kerana tiada stesen LRT di Mont Kiara. Bus stesen paling dekat di Hartamas Regency kondominium. Bus yang lalu di lokasi itu ialah bus Rapid KL U83. MRT bus ialah MRT T852 from Pusat Bandar Damansara MRT Stesen dan Bus MRT ialah T821 dan MRT T101 dari Semantan MRT Stesen.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Dibuka untuk semua Sarjana Muda atau Diploma atau Sijil atau Jurusan yang setara dalam sebarang Disiplin Seni atau Sains</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p>***</p><p>Kindly refer to the job description as below:</p><p>We are looking for candidates to join our Vertiqas Capital: <strong>Internship Program</strong>.</p><p>We welcome all students looking for internships as part of completing your diploma or undergraduate degree.</p><p>You should have a good command of English and interested to join a youthful and energetic organisation.</p><p>Requirements:</p><p>1. Undergraduate or degree or diploma or certificate or equivalent majoring in Business / Economics/ Property Management / Accounts or any Art or Science Discipline.</p><p>2. We are looking for independent, creative, mature, hardworking, eager to learn, energetic, pleasant personality and friendly and equip with good Microsoft office skills.</p><p>3. Candidate must be dynamic with good self-confidence and good communication skills as they will be dealing with our High Net worth Client.&nbsp;</p><p>4. You will participate in all business management in the company. Assist in business administration. Do market research. Analyse peer competitors. Create business proposal from the researched done.</p><p>5. The intern must have own transport as our Solaris Mont Kiara office is not accessible via public transport at all. The nearest bus stand is at Hartamas Regency condominium and you need to walk to Solaris Mont Kiara. The bus is Rapid KL U83. MRT bus is MRT T852 from Pusat Bandar Damansara MRT Station. MRT bus is MRT T821, MRT T101 from Semantan MRT Station.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>For those who are interested, please email your&nbsp;</p><p><strong>a) Resume and </strong></p><p><strong>b) Internship duration</strong></p><p>To genlauproperty36@gmail.com</p><p>Office hour is Monday-Friday 9:30 am-6:30 pm only</p><p>Monthly Allowance is RM500</p><p>* Only shortlisted candidate will be called for an interview*</p><p>This internship position is open all year to all certificate, diploma and degree holder who is keen to participate in our intern / internship / latihan praktikal / latihan industri / practical training / industrial training&nbsp;</p><p>Other Terms &amp; Conditions:&nbsp; <strong>Must have own transport or take bus as there is no</strong> <strong>LRT station at Mont Kiara. Nearest MRT station is Semantan or Pusat Bandar Damansara </strong></p><p>Undergraduate or diploma or certificate equivalent majoring in any Art or Science Disipline.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '<p>This internship position is open all year to all certificate, diploma and degree holder who is keen to participate in our intern / internship / latihan praktikal / latihan industri / practical training / industrial training</p>', '', NULL, '', 'MYR', '500.00', '500.00', 0, 0, '2017-12-17 20:32:11', '2017-12-27 20:39:21', '2018-05-01', 'post', 0, 0, NULL),
(153, 'Internship for Marketing Students', 953, 0, 5, '0', 2, '', 0, '', '', '<ul></ul><p>We are an MSC-status company listed on the Main Board of Bursa Malaysia, and is also the Asia/Pacific region&rsquo;s leading end-to-end payment services enabler that deploys world-class payment infrastructure, services and technology. GHL Systems&rsquo; complete portfolio of payment solutions include transaction routers and concentrators, terminal line encryption technologies, loyalty and online payment solutions, smartcard technologies, secure EDC networks and terminals to consulting services.</p><p>Our payment solutions are further recognized, accredited and certified by organizations and governing bodies such as Visa, MasterCard, JCB, MEPS, SIRIM and the Line Encryption Working Group.&nbsp;</p><p>By providing a broad range of services across the payment solutions spectrum, GHL Systems today deploys its products and services to multiple clients spread across various vertical segments - not limited to banking and financial services institutions, telecommunications, transportation, retail and oil and gas.</p><p>We are now urgently looking for&nbsp;<strong>Internship for Maketing Students </strong>with the below requirements: -</p><ul><li>Candidate must possess or currently pursuing a Diploma or Bachelor&#39;s Degree in Business Studies/Administration/Management, Marketing or equivalent.</li><li>Required language(s): English.</li><li>Preferred language(s): Bahasa Malaysia, Chinese.</li><li>1 Internship position(s) for duration of 3 month(s).</li><li>Training location: Bandar Sri Damansara, Kepong.</li><li>Able to join immediately.</li></ul><p>Any interested candidates please fax, e-mail with cover letter, completed resume, certificates / relevant documents and 1 recent passport-sized photograph to the below address: -</p><p><strong>GHL SYSTEMS BERHAD</strong><br />Human Resource Department<br />C-G-15, Block C, Jalan Dataran SD1,<br />Dataran SD, PJU 9 Bandar Sri Damansara,<br />52200 Kuala Lumpur,<br />Malaysia.&nbsp;<br /><br />Tel: 603-6286 3388<br />Fax: 603-6280 2999<br />Email:&nbsp;hr@ghl.com</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', '800.00', '800.00', 0, 0, '2018-01-02 23:15:43', '2018-01-02 23:15:43', '2018-05-01', 'post', 0, 0, NULL);
