luded as value added services with Advertisement packages.</p>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"col-sm-6 col-sm-pull-6 g-promo-section-img-right-md g-promo-section-img-left-md g-bg-position-center g-height-400-xs g-height-100-percent-md js-fullwidth-img\" style=\"background-image: url(assets/img/site/sponsored-employers.png);\">\r\n                    <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"assets/img/site/sponsored-employers.png\" alt=\"Image\" style=\"display: none;\">\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <!--========== END SERVICES ==========-->', '2018-01-31 03:36:58', '2018-01-31 03:36:58'),
