(15, 551, '', 46, '', '', '', '40000', 'Shah Alam, Selangor', 5, 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '2016-04-11 22:38:24', '2016-04-11 22:53:28', '', '', '', '', '0', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Youbeli.com', 'Youbeli.com was created in year 2009,  aiming to be the most visited online shopping site in Malaysia, which provides excellence, convenient services, where customers can find and discover anything they might want to buy online, by offering them the lowest possible prices.\r\n\r\n\r\nIn 2011, Youbeli.com began to offer its e-commerce platform to other retailers and individual sellers to join the Youbeli WebStore program. Today, Youbeli.com is one of the top B2B2C marketplace in Malaysia, which provides the platform, traffic and expertise to help retailers to set up their businesses online. Hundreds of retailers and individual sellers have managed to increase their sales and reach new customers by leveraging on Youbeli’s e-commerce platform.\r\n\r\n\r\nWebStore merchants leverage on Youbeli.com as an incremental sales channel for their new merchandise and empower their e-commerce offerings from end-to-end, including ready purchase customer based, technology services, data entry, graphic design, photo shooting, inventory control and order fulfillment such as customer service and goods packing services.\r\n\r\n\r\nYoubeli’s evolution from an e-commerce website to B2B2C online marketplace and retail partner to e-commerce solution platform is driven by the spirit of providing excellence convenience to both retailers and customers. We believe technology will change the way people do their daily shopping and we endeavor to research and develop new technologies to improve the lives of our customers: retailers, sellers, business owners, and shoppers around the world. That\'s where we are heading, to be the most visited online shopping place in Malaysia.', '', 'http://www.youbeli.com', '1800 88 2354', '', '', '9:00 - 19:00', '', 'Casual', 'Medical, travel', 'Engli